high_descs: Turn left, walk to the edge of the countertop, then turn left and walk up to the sink.
Pick up the yellow handled knife that is in the sink.
Turn to the right, walk to the wall, then turn right and walk up to the table.
Slice the potato that is on the counter.
Turn to the right, move forward a bit, then turn to the right again to go to the kitchen sink.
Place the knife down in the kitchen sink.
Turn to the right, walk to the wall, then turn right again and walk up to the kitchen table.
Pick up a slice of potato from the kitchen table.
Turn to the right, move forward, then right again to walk over to the kitchen sink.
Rinse off the potato slice in the sink before taking it out again.
Turn to the right, walk to the end of the countertop, then turn right again and walk forward, walk to the wall, then turn left to face the table.
Place the slice of potato down on the table, to the left of the tomato.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean slice of potato on the kitchen table.
